### Finance Backend API Test Requests
# Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Login to get a JWT token
POST http://localhost:3000/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finance.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Create a new user (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "analyst2@finance.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ANALYST"
}

### Get all users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a user role/status (Admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "VIEWER",
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### Delete a user (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a record (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "notes": "April Salary"
}

### Get records with filters (Admin / Analyst)
GET http://localhost:3000/records?type=INCOME&category=Salary&startDate=2026-04-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2026-04-30T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a record (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:3000/records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5500,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Updated Salary"
}

### Delete a record (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get dashboard summary
GET http://localhost:3000/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get category totals
GET http://localhost:3000/dashboard/category-totals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get monthly trends
GET http://localhost:3000/dashboard/monthly-trends
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
